.description
Part 2 of a 2 part release of the very popular program by Stefan Becker.
This part contains an LHA archive of the source, TeX docs and programmer's
support files.  Part 1 can be found on disk number 872.  ToolManager is a
full featured program for either WorkBench or CLI tool management.
Includes the ability to add menu items to the 2.x "Tools" menu, add
WorkBench icons or dock Windows.  Features multi-column docks that
automatically detect largest image size, ARexx, sound and Locale support.
Lots of graphic images, and programmer's support for using the
toolmanager.library.  Requires 2.x for full functionality.  
